response.overview: A real human being and a real hero, finds himself at Tiananmen, Square and later in Moscow on a revenge plot to kill the ogre from Shrek 3. Eventually, he comes across a young broad named Jeniquiasolo, who is later revealed to be a male prostitute. Once revealed, the real human being and a real hero, kills Jeniquiasolo for misleading him. The Oakland raiders football team get involved and try to hunt down and kill him, while he spends his days at a male strip club, wondering if he will ever get revenge for his dead sisters grandmothers best friend Tululuqie.
